<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .success-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .success-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .success-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .success-header p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .step-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3182ce;
            color: white;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .step-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .step-description {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .install-button {
            background: #24292e;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .install-button:hover {
            background: #1a1e23;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(36, 41, 46, 0.3);
        }
        
        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            color: #4a5568;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .feature-list li::before {
            content: 'âœ“';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #38a169;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .support-section {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .support-section h3 {
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .support-section p {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .support-section a {
            color: #3182ce;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .support-section a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .plan-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #38a169;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .welcome-message {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .welcome-message h2 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .welcome-message p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <!-- Welcome Message -->
        <div class="welcome-message">
            <h2>ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to GetYourTester!</h2>
            <p>You're now subscribed to the <strong><%= plan %></strong> plan</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Success Header -->
        <div class="success-header">
            <h1>Let's Connect Ovi to Your GitHub</h1>
            <p>Follow these simple steps to get started with AI-powered QA</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 1: Install GitHub App -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3 class="step-title">Install the GitHub App (1 minute)</h3>
            <p class="step-description">Click the button below and choose the org/repos where you want Ovi to run.</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/apps/getyourtester/installations/new" class="install-button">
                <i class="fab fa-github me-2"></i>Install Ovi on GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2: Create/Update PR -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3 class="step-title">Open/Update a PR</h3>
            <p class="step-description">After installation, open a new PR or push to an existing one. Ovi will post an automated review comment with:</p>
            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Readiness score</li>
                <li>Specific risks</li>
                <li>Test Recipe (happy path + critical path)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Support Section -->
        <div class="support-section">
            <h3>Need help or want human QA on a release?</h3>
            <p>Email us at <strong><a href="mailto:support@getyourtester.com">support@getyourtester.com</a></strong> with the PR link and "Human QA" in the subject.</p>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">What if I need an invoice or to cancel?</h3>
            <p>Reply to your Stripe receipt email or <a href="mailto:support@getyourtester.com">contact support</a> â€” we handle it same-day.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Additional Resources -->
        <div class="step-card">
            <h3 class="step-title">ðŸ“š Getting Started Resources</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>Documentation</h5>
                    <p><a href="/docs" class="text-decoration-none">ðŸ“– Read our complete guide</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>Demo Call</h5>
                    <p><a href="https://calendly.com/qakarma/discovery" class="text-decoration-none" target="_blank">ðŸ“… Schedule a walkthrough</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
